
A handy utility to pop up an xlogo as the decimal seconds 
since epoch aligns itself with 1234567890

This utility will pass usefulness on 13 February. Then we'll have to update it for May 2033 or something I think.

utility.sh - More thoughtful version.

8,11,12 February 2009 by Dale Anderson
